00:55:50.120 --> 00:55:54.080
[Guest]: to you know, pro market reforms, a lot of upward mobility, which has happened is a far

00:55:54.080 --> 00:56:01.120
[Guest]: more democratized place, in terms of opportunities, and ideas also, they will not listen to the

00:56:01.120 --> 00:56:07.000
[Guest]: old elite, they wanted I mean, I've seen in front of my own eyes in Delhi, you know, something

00:56:07.000 --> 00:56:08.480
[Guest]: like an Ahmadi party growing up.

00:56:08.480 --> 00:56:12.400
[Guest]: Now, I do not know where the Ahmadi party will go from here in the next election five

00:56:12.400 --> 00:56:16.200
