00:56:27.560 --> 00:56:34.120
[Guest]: up as a political force capture the imagination of power, I think it also shows how open possibilities

00:56:34.120 --> 00:56:36.120
[Guest]: of building alternative politics are.

00:56:36.120 --> 00:56:40.520
[Guest]: And those kinds of options are open to everybody, I mean, it is not just that the BJP only circulates

00:56:40.520 --> 00:56:41.520
